# This directory contains patches to apply to the upstream Buck2 prelude.
#
# Patches are applied in alphabetical order.
# Use numbered prefixes for ordering: 01-fix-something.patch, 02-add-feature.patch
#
# To create a patch:
#   1. Clone facebook/buck2-prelude
#   2. Make your changes
#   3. git diff > /path/to/turnkey/nix/patches/prelude/01-description.patch
